Known Issues
- when deleting a transfer, quantity left for the transfer in location may become negative
- when deleting a restock, quantity left for the location may become negative
- in stock/restock, if user diliberately not entering amount, crash will happen
- delete products/manufacturers will be a problem for stock/restock/purchase
- if new purchase item is not created due to error, stock/product might be changed
